Paul Kelly (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Kelly_(actor) 0 Paul Michael Kelly (August 9, 1899 – November 6, 1956) was an American stage, film and television actor. His career survived a manslaughter conviction, tied to a sex scandal, that caused him to spend time in prison in the late 1920s.
